OL,3,CBereaved families meeting to discuss
OL,4,Chopes for public inquiry into health
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FBereaved families who have lost loved
OL,8,Fones under the region's biggest mental
OL,9,Fhealth trust are meeting for the first
OL,10,Ftime, after the government announced
OL,11,Fthere would be a public inquiry into
OL,12,Fthe trust.
OL,14,FIn December, Health Secretary Wes
OL,15,FStreeting announced that a statutory
OL,16,Finquiry into the Tees, Esk and Wear
OL,17,FValleys NHS Trust was the best way for
OL,18,Fbereaved families to get the
OL,19,Faccountability and truth they deserve.
