OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FA statutory inquiry will compel trust
OL,8,Fstaff, past and present, to give
OL,9,Fevidence.
OL,11,FAround 80 people are due to meet at
OL,12,Ftheir solicitors' office in
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough to discuss what
OL,14,Fquestions they would like the inquiry
OL,15,Fto answer, and the kind of person they
OL,16,Fwould like to lead it, for example a
OL,17,Fhigh court judge or a medical
OL,18,Fprofessional.
