OL,7,FIt has been organised by the legal
OL,8,Ffirm Ison Harrison, and solicitor
OL,9,FAlistair Smith said it is important
OL,10,Ffor families to have their say as the
OL,11,Finquiry is set up.
OL,13,F"Mr Streeting wants families to have
OL,14,Fan input into the terms of reference
OL,15,Fto this inquiry," he said.
OL,17,F"What do they want the inquiry to
OL,18,Fcover, what went wrong, how did it go
OL,19,Fwrong and why did other people like
OL,20,FNHS England or the Care Quality
OL,21,FCommission not step in?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
