OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,F"More importantly how can we put
OL,8,Fthings right so you've got a good
OL,9,Ffunctioning trust which isn't there at
OL,10,Fthe moment."
OL,12,FSome of the families will then meet
OL,13,Fwith the government to share their
OL,14,Fviews, with a decision on who will
OL,15,Flead the inquiry expected by the end
OL,16,Fof February.
