OL,7,FAlison Smith, chief executive at the
OL,8,Ftrust, said: "Since joining the trust,
OL,9,FI have met and continue to meet
OL,10,Fpatients and their loved ones who
OL,11,Fbravely and passionately shared their
OL,12,Fstories. This includes occasions where
OL,13,Fwe didn't get things right.
OL,15,F"With the public inquiry now
OL,16,Fconfirmed, we will fully support the
OL,17,Fprocess with transparency, openness
OL,18,Fand humility.
