OL,7,F"Above all, we are committed to
OL,8,Flistening, reflecting, and taking
OL,9,Fmeaningful action to improve the
OL,10,Fexperiences for our patients,
OL,11,Ffamilies, carers and staff. And
OL,12,Fimportantly, so those who have been
OL,13,Faffected hear how sorry we are."
